item.title: Design & UX Reading List
item.description: Various readings and learnings about design. Usually with some kind of Open Source overlap or context. Trauma & design PubPub: Some basic definitions key to understanding the relationship between trauma and design. Maintained by KJ Hepworth, Kat Lo, Eriol Fox, and Shirin Mori. Ushahidi Open Design, maintained by Eriol Fox: A collection of resources, notes, and other written content for distributed, asynchronous design contributions to software projects.
